data.description:
Welcome to your serene retreat nestled on 3.34 acres of picturesque landscape with stunning lake frontages! This delightful property offers the perfect blend of tranquility, space, and potential. Located in a napoleon schools, this home promises a lifestyle of comfort and convenience.
Step inside to discover a warm and inviting living space filled with natural light. The main level boasts a cozy living room, a well-appointed kitchen with ample cabinet space, and a dining area perfect for gatherings. 3 beds 2.5 bath with a basement kitchen to boot.
Outside, the sprawling grounds offer endless possibilities. Whether you're in the 24*40 pole barn, overlooking the tranquil lake,  or hosting outdoor barbecues, this property provides the ultimate setting for enjoying nature's beauty
